1. Overview

â€œMakeUp Quizâ€ is a no-subscription, offline, in-classroom quiz management application designed to promote honesty, integrity, and fairness during quizzes and tests. It enables teachers to create, manage, and administer paperless quizzes even in areas with limited or no internet connectivity.

